{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Tutorial Completo: Análisis de Yield Curves con bonos-lib\n",
    "\n",
    "## Análisis profesional de la curva de rendimiento de bonos del gobierno británico (Gilts)\n",
    "\n",
    "Este tutorial te mostrará cómo usar **bonos-lib** para calcular, analizar e interpretar curvas de rendimiento reales usando datos de mercado."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Instalar y importar librerías"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!pip install bonos-lib -q"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "from datetime import datetime\n",
    "from bonos_lib import YieldCurveCalculator, LinearInterpolator\n",
    "\n",
    "# Configurar estilos para gráficos profesionales\n",
    "sns.set_style('whitegrid')\n",
    "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (14, 7)\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.size'] = 10"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Datos reales de Gilts (Bonos del Gobierno Británico)\n",
    "\n",
    "Fuente: Mercado de bonos del gobierno británico - April 2026\n",
    "\n",
    "Convertimos los rendimientos de mercado a precios de bonos cupón cero usando:\n",
    "$$Precio = \\frac{100}{(1 + Rendimiento)^{años}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Datos reales de Gilts - Rendimientos de mercado\n",
    "data_gilts = {\n",
    "    'plazo': ['3M', '6M', '12M', '2Y', '5Y', '10Y', '30Y'],\n",
    "    'dias': [90, 180, 360, 720, 1800, 3600, 10800],\n",
    "    'rendimiento_pct': [3.60, 3.60, 3.60, 3.88, 3.88, 4.13, 4.75]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "df_gilts = pd.DataFrame(data_gilts)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Convertir rendimientos a precios de cupón cero\n",
    "# Precio = 100 / (1 + rendimiento)^(días/360)\n",
    "df_gilts['rendimiento'] = df_gilts['rendimiento_pct'] / 100\n",
    "df_gilts['precio'] = 100 / (1 + df_gilts['rendimiento']) ** (df_gilts['dias'] / 360)\n",
    "df_gilts['años'] = df_gilts['dias'] / 360\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(\"DATOS DE GILTS - BONOS DEL GOBIERNO BRITÁNICO\")\n",
    "print(\"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(df_gilts[['plazo', 'dias', 'años', 'rendimiento_pct', 'precio']].to_string(index=False))\n",
    "print(\"\\nInterpretación:\")\n",
    "print(\"- Un bono de 3 meses con rendimiento 3.60% se vende a 99.11 (descuento de 0.89)\")\n",
    "print(\"- Un bono de 30 años con rendimiento 4.75% se vende a 21.48 (descuento de 78.52)\")\n",
    "print(\"\\nNota: El descuento aumenta con el plazo debido a los mayores períodos de actualización\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Calcular la Yield Curve\n",
    "\n",
    "La **yield curve** (curva de rendimiento) muestra la relación entre el plazo de vencimiento y el rendimiento anual de un bono."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Crear calculator con datos de cupón cero\n",
    "calc = YieldCurveCalculator(nominal=100, days_year=360)\n",
    "\n",
    "# DataFrame para calcular yields\n",
    "bonos_data = df_gilts[['dias', 'precio']].copy()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calcular yields (verificar que coinciden con nuestros datos)\n",
    "yields_df = calc.calculate_yields(bonos_data)\n",
    "yields_df['plazo'] = df_gilts['plazo'].values\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(\"YIELD CURVE CALCULADA\")\n",
    "print(\"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(yields_df[['plazo', 'dias', 'precio', 'yield']].assign(\n",
    "    yield_pct=yields_df['yield'] * 100\n",
    ")[['plazo', 'dias', 'precio', 'yield_pct']].to_string(index=False))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nRango de tasas: {yields_df['yield'].min()*100:.2f}% - {yields_df['yield'].max()*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "print(f\"Pendiente de la curva: {(yields_df['yield'].iloc[-1] - yields_df['yield'].iloc[0])*100:.2f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Visualización 1: Curva de Rendimiento Básica"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gráfico 1: Yield Curve\n",
    "ax1.plot(yields_df['dias']/360, yields_df['yield']*100, 'o-', \n",
    "         linewidth=3, markersize=10, color='#1f77b4', label='Yield Curve')\n",
    "ax1.fill_between(yields_df['dias']/360, yields_df['yield']*100, alpha=0.3, color='#1f77b4')\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel('Plazo (años)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.set_ylabel('Rendimiento (%)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.set_title('Yield Curve de Gilts - April 2026', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')\n",
    "ax1.legend(fontsize=11, loc='best')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Añadir valores en los puntos\n",
    "for i, row in yields_df.iterrows():\n",
    "    ax1.annotate(f\"{row['yield']*100:.2f}%\", \n",
    "                xy=(row['dias']/360, row['yield']*100),\n",
    "                xytext=(5, 5), textcoords='offset points', fontsize=9)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gráfico 2: Precios de bonos\n",
    "colors = plt.cm.RdYlGn(np.linspace(0.2, 0.8, len(yields_df)))\n",
    "bars = ax2.bar(yields_df['plazo'], yields_df['precio'], color=colors, edgecolor='black', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "ax2.axhline(y=100, color='red', linestyle='--', linewidth=2, label='Valor nominal')\n",
    "ax2.set_xlabel('Plazo', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.set_ylabel('Precio', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.set_title('Precio de Bonos Cupón Cero por Plazo', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y', linestyle='--')\n",
    "ax2.legend(fontsize=11)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Añadir valores en las barras\n",
    "for bar in bars:\n",
    "    height = bar.get_height()\n",
    "    ax2.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., height,\n",
    "            f'{height:.2f}', ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=9, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Interpretación:\")\n",
    "print(\"- La curva tiene pendiente positiva (upward sloping): tasas más altas para plazos más largos\")\n",
    "print(\"- Los precios disminuyen con el plazo (relación inversa con el rendimiento)\")\n",
    "print(\"- El desplazamiento de precio es mayor en plazos más largos\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Interpolación de Tasas\n",
    "\n",
    "La interpolación nos permite obtener tasas para plazos intermedios no observados en el mercado."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Crear interpolador\n",
    "interpolator = LinearInterpolator()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Interpolar para plazos específicos\n",
    "plazos_interpolados = [60, 120, 240, 450, 900, 1800, 5400]\n",
    "tasas_interpoladas = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "for plazo in plazos_interpolados:\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        tasa = calc.interpolate(yields_df, plazo)\n",
    "        tasas_interpoladas[plazo] = tasa\n",
    "    except ValueError as e:\n",
    "        print(f\"Error para {plazo} días: {e}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Crear tabla de interpolación\n",
    "df_interpolado = pd.DataFrame([\n",
    "    {\n",
    "        'dias': días,\n",
    "        'años': días/360,\n",
    "        'rendimiento_pct': tasa*100,\n",
    "        'tipo': 'Interpolado'\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    for días, tasa in tasas_interpoladas.items()\n",
    "])\n",
    "\n",
    "df_observado = yields_df[['dias', 'yield']].copy()\n",
    "df_observado.columns = ['dias', 'rendimiento_pct']\n",
    "df_observado['rendimiento_pct'] = df_observado['rendimiento_pct'] * 100\n",
    "df_observado['años'] = df_observado['dias'] / 360\n",
    "df_observado['tipo'] = 'Observado'\n",
    "\n",
    "# Combinar para visualización\n",
    "df_curva_completa = pd.concat([df_observado, df_interpolado], ignore_index=True)\n",
    "df_curva_completa = df_curva_completa.sort_values('dias').reset_index(drop=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(\"TASAS INTERPOLADAS\")\n",
    "print(\"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(df_interpolado[['dias', 'años', 'rendimiento_pct']].to_string(index=False))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nTotal de puntos en la curva: {len(yields_df)} observados + {len(df_interpolado)} interpolados = {len(df_curva_completa)} puntos\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Visualización 2: Curva Interpolada Detallada"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Crear una curva más detallada usando interpolación de rango\n",
    "curve_detailed = interpolator.interpolate_range(yields_df, min_days=90, max_days=10800, step=30)\n",
    "curve_detailed['años'] = curve_detailed['dias'] / 360\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(14, 7))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Curva interpolada\n",
    "ax.plot(curve_detailed['años'], curve_detailed['yield']*100, '-', \n",
    "        linewidth=2.5, color='#2ca02c', label='Interpolación lineal', alpha=0.8)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Puntos observados\n",
    "ax.scatter(yields_df['dias']/360, yields_df['yield']*100, \n",
    "          s=150, color='red', zorder=5, edgecolors='darkred', linewidth=2, label='Datos observados')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Llenar área bajo la curva\n",
    "ax.fill_between(curve_detailed['años'], curve_detailed['yield']*100, alpha=0.2, color='#2ca02c')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Línea de referencia\n",
    "ax.axhline(y=yields_df['yield'].mean()*100, color='gray', linestyle='--', \n",
    "          linewidth=2, alpha=0.5, label=f\"Media: {yields_df['yield'].mean()*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Plazo (años)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Rendimiento (%)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_title('Yield Curve Interpolada - Gilts 2026', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')\n",
    "ax.legend(fontsize=11, loc='best')\n",
    "ax.set_xlim(0, 30)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✓ Curva interpolada con 30 puntos intermedios\")\n",
    "print(f\"✓ Rango: {curve_detailed['años'].min():.2f} - {curve_detailed['años'].max():.2f} años\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Bootstrapping: Calcular Tasas Forward"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calcular tasas forward mediante bootstrapping\n",
    "forwards_df = calc.bootstrap(yields_df)\n",
    "forwards_df['plazo'] = df_gilts['plazo'].values\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(\"TASAS SPOT Y FORWARD (BOOTSTRAPPING)\")\n",
    "print(\"═\" * 80)\n",
    "print(forwards_df[['plazo', 'dias', 'spot_rate', 'forward_rate']].assign(\n",
    "    spot_pct=forwards_df['spot_rate']*100,\n",
    "    forward_pct=forwards_df['forward_rate']*100\n",
    ")[['plazo', 'dias', 'spot_pct', 'forward_pct']].round(4).to_string(index=False))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nInterpretación del Bootstrapping:\")\n",
    "print(\"- Tasa Spot (Z): Tasa actual para un plazo específico\")\n",
    "print(\"- Tasa Forward: Tasa implícita para un período futuro\")\n",
    "print(\"\\nEjemplo:\")\n",
    "print(f\"  • Tasa spot a 1 año: {forwards_df.loc[2, 'spot_rate']*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "print(f\"  • Tasa forward 1-2 años: {forwards_df.loc[3, 'forward_rate']*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "print(f\"  • Interpretación: Si hoy tasa a 1 año = {forwards_df.loc[2, 'spot_rate']*100:.2f}%\")\n",
    "print(f\"                   El mercado implica tasa de 1-2 años = {forwards_df.loc[3, 'forward_rate']*100:.2f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 8. Visualización 3: Análisis de Tasas Spot vs Forward"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code">
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 6))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gráfico 1: Comparación Spot vs Forward\n",
    "x_pos = np.arange(len(forwards_df))\n",
    "width = 0.35\n",
    "\n",
    "bars1 = ax1.bar(x_pos - width/2, forwards_df['spot_rate']*100, width, \n",
    "                label='Tasa Spot', color='#1f77b4', alpha=0.8, edgecolor='black')\n",
    "bars2 = ax1.bar(x_pos + width/2, forwards_df['forward_rate']*100, width,\n",
    "                label='Tasa Forward', color='#ff7f0e', alpha=0.8, edgecolor='black')\n",
    "\n",
    "ax1.set_xlabel('Plazo', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.set_ylabel('Tasa (%)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.set_title('Comparación: Tasas Spot vs Forward', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax1.set_xticks(x_pos)\n",
    "ax1.set_xticklabels(forwards_df['plazo'])\n",
    "ax1.legend(fontsize=11)\n",
    "ax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Valores en barras\n",
    "for bar in bars1:\n",
    "    height = bar.get_height()\n",
    "    ax1.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., height,\n",
    "            f'{height:.2f}%', ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=8)\n",
    "for bar in bars2:\n",
    "    height = bar.get_height()\n",
    "    ax1.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., height,\n",
    "            f'{height:.2f}%', ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=8)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gráfico 2: Diferencial Forward (Forward - Spot)\n",
    "diferencial = (forwards_df['forward_rate'] - forwards_df['spot_rate']) * 100\n",
    "colors_diff = ['green' if x > 0 else 'red' for x in diferencial]\n",
    "\n",
    "bars3 = ax2.bar(forwards_df['plazo'], diferencial, color=colors_diff, alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "ax2.axhline(y=0, color='black', linestyle='-', linewidth=1)\n",
    "ax2.set_xlabel('Plazo', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.set_ylabel('Diferencial (pb)', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.set_title('Forward Rate - Spot Rate (Puntos Base)', fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Valores en barras\n",
    "for i, (bar, val) in enumerate(zip(bars3, diferencial)):\n",
    "    height = bar.get_height()\n",
    "    y_pos = height if height > 0 else height\n",
    "    ax2.text(bar.get_x() + bar.get_width()/2., y_pos,\n",
    "            f'{val:.1f}', ha='center', va='bottom' if height > 0 else 'top', fontsize=9, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nObservaciones:\")\n",
    "print(f\"- Diferencial promedio: {diferencial.mean():.2f} pb\")\n",
    "print(f\"- Máximo diferencial: {diferencial.max():.2f} pb (esperado en plazos largos)\")\n",
    "print(f\"- Mínimo diferencial: {diferencial.min():.2f} pb\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 9. Visualización 4: Factores de Descuento y Análisis Avanzado"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calcular factores de descuento (Discount Factors)\n",
    "yields_df['discount_factor'] = 1 / (1 + yields_df['yield']) ** (yields_df['dias'] / 360)\n",
    "yields_df['valor_presente_100'] = 100 * yields_df['discount_factor']\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calcular volatilidad y duración modificada\n",
    "yields_df['duration'] = yields_df['dias'] / 360  # Para cupón cero, duration = tiempo a vencimiento\n",
    "yields_df['modified_duration'] = yields_df['duration'] / (1 + yields_df['yield'])\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(16, 12))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 1. Factores de Descuento\n",
    "ax = axes[0, 0]\n",
    "ax.plot(yields_df['dias']/360, yields_df['discount_factor'], 'o-', \n",
    "       linewidth=2.5, markersize=8, color='#d62728')\n",
    "ax.fill_between(yields_df['dias']/360, yields_df['discount_factor'], alpha=0.3, color='#d62728')\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Plazo (años)', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Factor de Descuento', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_title('Factores de Descuento por Plazo', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "ax.set_ylim(0, 1.05)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. Duración Modificada\n",
    "ax = axes[0, 1]\n",
    "ax.bar(yields_df['plazo'], yields_df['modified_duration'], \n",
    "      color='#9467bd', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Plazo', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Duración Modificada (años)', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_title('Duración Modificada - Sensibilidad a Tasas', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, axis='y')\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, (x, y) in enumerate(zip(yields_df['plazo'], yields_df['modified_duration'])):\n",
    "    ax.text(i, y, f'{y:.2f}', ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=9, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. Relación Yield vs Duration\n",
    "ax = axes[1, 0]\n",
    "scatter = ax.scatter(yields_df['yield']*100, yields_df['modified_duration'], \n",
    "                    s=200, c=yields_df['dias'], cmap='viridis', \n",
    "                    edgecolors='black', linewidth=2, alpha=0.7)\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Rendimiento (%)', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Duración Modificada', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_title('Relación: Rendimiento vs Duración', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "cbar = plt.colorbar(scatter, ax=ax)\n",
    "cbar.set_label('Días', fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Añadir etiquetas de plazo\n",
    "for i, plazo in enumerate(yields_df['plazo']):\n",
    "    ax.annotate(plazo, (yields_df['yield'].iloc[i]*100, yields_df['modified_duration'].iloc[i]),\n",
    "               xytext=(5, 5), textcoords='offset points', fontsize=9, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 4. Distribución de tasas\n",
    "ax = axes[1, 1]\n",
    "ax.hist(yields_df['yield']*100, bins=7, color='#1f77b4', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "ax.axvline(yields_df['yield'].mean()*100, color='red', linestyle='--', linewidth=2.5, label='Media')\n",
    "ax.axvline(yields_df['yield'].median()*100, color='green', linestyle='--', linewidth=2.5, label='Mediana')\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Rendimiento (%)', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Frecuencia', fontsize=11, fontweight='bold')\n",
